Basic Homer API 0.1 (REST/JSON - development only)

-------------------------------------
Legend Parameters:

[] = Mandatory
{} = Optional

-------------------------------------

session: 	Returns SIP messages by Session-ID
		REST: /api/session/[SESSION-ID]/{FROM_DATE}/{TO_DATE}/{LIMIT RESULTS}
		Equivalent:	api.php?task=session&cid=&fd=&td=&limit=


msg: 		Returns a single SIP message by ID
		REST: /api/msg/[MSG-ID]/{FROM_DATE}/{TO_DATE}
		Equivalent:	api.php?task=msg&id=&fd=&td=


last: 		Returns last X SIP messages
		REST: /api/last/{limit}
		Equivalent:	api.php?task=last&limit=
		Example:	/api/last/5

search: 	Returns matching SIP messages
		REST: /api/search/[FIELD]/[VALUE]
		Equivalent:	api.php?task=search&field=&value=&limit=&hours=
		Example:	/api/search/method/401&limit=2&hours=6

stat-total:	Returns Total Packet Counter
		REST: (tbd)
		api/api.php?task=statscount&method=ALL

stat-measure:	Returns ASR/NER for current sampling cycle
		REST: (tbd)
		api/api.php?task=statscount&method=ALL&measure=1

stat-current:	Returns Counter for current sampling cycle
		REST: (tbd)
		api/api.php?task=statscount&method=CURRENT&hours=

stat-methods:	Returns Values for Call Events
		REST: (tbd)
		api/api.php?task=statscount&method=INVITE&hours=

stat-register:	Returns Values for Registartion Events
		REST: (tbd)
		api/api.php?task=statscount&method=REGISTRATION&hours=


	..to be continued..


